<% content_for(:title) do %>
    Bug
<% end %>

<h2 class="subhead"><span>Bugs</span></h2>

<div class="post">
    <div class="posthead">
        <h3>Please tell us what we are doing wrong!</h3>
    </div>
    <p>If it is an issue with the content server (Priv.ly), make sure you include the URL with the error and a description of the problem.</p>
    <p>If it is an issue with a particular website, make sure you include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>The version of the extension you were using (if any)</li>
        <li>A link to the host page with a public Priv.ly link</li>
        <li>Your browser name and version</li>
        <li>Your operating system</li>
        <li>A description of the behavior</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Once you gather the relevant information, submit an issue to the relevant system below. Thanks!</p>
    <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "Firefox Extension Issues", "https://github.com/smcgregor/privly-firefox/issues" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Content Server Issues (this site)", "https://github.com/smcgregor/privly-web/issues" %></li>
    </ul>
    
</div>


